flowchart LR
    A[Application log output] --> B[stdout or stderr]
    B --> C[App Service container runtime]
    C --> D[Docker log files<br/>home LogFiles docker]
    C --> E[Application filesystem logs<br/>home LogFiles Application]
    C --> F[Application Insights or Azure Monitor Logs]

    D -. Rolling .-> G[Quick incident investigation]
    E -. e.g. 7 days 100MB retention .-> H[Short-term archive]
    F -. e.g. 90+ days configurable .-> I[Long-term storage trend analysis alerts]
